1
00:00:04,570 --> 00:00:07,240
I worked as a salaryman
for a toxic company,

2
00:00:07,240 --> 00:00:09,070
until I reincarnated...

3
00:00:09,070 --> 00:00:12,910
in a crazy world where everything
is dropped by monsters in dungeons.

4
00:00:13,410 --> 00:00:18,330
In my new life, I'm level 1,
but I have a unique skill

5
00:00:18,330 --> 00:00:20,540
that puts all of my drop rates at rank S.

6
00:00:21,210 --> 00:00:23,210
And today I'm facing off against...

7
00:00:23,210 --> 00:00:24,880
a rare monster?!

8
00:00:24,880 --> 00:00:28,550
I had no idea drops from monsters
could be used that way!

9
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:45,230
MY UNIQUE SKILL MAKES ME OP EVEN AT LEVEL 1

10
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:05,020
MOVING TO A NEW PLACE!
JUST RELAXING AT HOME

11
00:02:05,020 --> 00:02:08,150
TELULU LEVEL 4

12
00:02:10,690 --> 00:02:13,740
Ah! That's a rare monster!

13
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:14,610
What?!

14
00:02:15,570 --> 00:02:17,030
You're not getting away!

15
00:02:22,210 --> 00:02:23,790
What's this?

16
00:02:23,790 --> 00:02:27,380
That's the first time I've seen
a rare monster drop anything!

17
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,090
Emily...

18
00:02:31,090 --> 00:02:32,260
Emily,

19
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:35,090
would you put this on?

20
00:02:35,550 --> 00:02:38,010
What? Y-You mean...

21
00:02:38,430 --> 00:02:41,350
I want you to have it.

22
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:45,940
You've made me so happy!
I'll treasure this!

23
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:47,440
Great!

24
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:50,230
Now you can rake in the profits for us!

25
00:02:50,230 --> 00:02:53,530
Huh? Rake in... profits?

26
00:02:53,530 --> 00:02:57,570
Oh, I guess you can't hear it,
like with the seeds and stuff.

27
00:02:57,570 --> 00:02:58,160
PUT ON, FIGHT AS USUAL, DOUBLE DROPS

28
