29
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:02,910
PUT ON, FIGHT AS USUAL, DOUBLE DROPS
It's apparently a necklace

30
00:03:02,910 --> 00:03:04,160
PUT ON, FIGHT AS USUAL, DOUBLE DROPS
