31
00:03:04,810 --> 00:03:06,620
That's the kind of thing...

32
00:03:06,620 --> 00:03:07,580
Emily?

33
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:11,170
That's the kind of thing
you need to say first!

34
00:03:11,170 --> 00:03:13,370
