35
00:03:19,390 --> 00:03:21,810
Wow, look at them all!

36
00:03:22,270 --> 00:03:25,060
This double drop rate is amazing!

37
00:03:33,390 --> 00:03:34,860
Can I help with anything?

38
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,780
That's all right.
I'll be done in no time.

39
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:41,870
