and get home at the usual time.

55
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:25,830
Good!

56
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,250
Is that...

57
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:38,550
Hmm... These are a bit
difficult to appraise.

58
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:40,640
You there.

59
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:44,140
Would you mind letting me
have those bamboo shoots?

60
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:44,970
Huh?

61
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:52,360
Uh, I mean, I don't mind
giving you one of them...

62
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:55,110
Thank you.
I'll just take one, then.

63
00:05:02,530 --> 00:05:04,450
Whoa, that was amazing!

64
00:05:11,620 --> 00:05:14,290
D-Does it taste that bad?

65
00:05:14,290 --> 00:05:17,170
Despite being raw,
it's not bitter at all!

66
00:05:17,170 --> 00:05:21,930
It's so juicy and sweet! I've never
had a bamboo shoot like this before!

67
00:05:21,930 --> 00:05:23,510
It's like... It's like...

68
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:27,640
a rare monster of flavor!

69
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:29,520
Who the heck is this lady?!

70
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:33,770
Please let me buy all of these
marvelous bamboo shoots.

71
00:05:33,770 --> 00:05:36,230
Huh? Uh, but these are...

72
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:40,360
I-It's all right!
She's welcome to have all of them!

73
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:43,160
Really? Well, okay, then.

74
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,450
Thank you!

75
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:48,870
I can't put a price on
this great flavor, so...

76
00:05:49,410 --> 00:05:52,540
Please accept this
as a token of my gratitude!

77
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:57,340
