Is she about to pay big for these?!

78
00:05:59,050 --> 00:05:59,960
Huh?

79
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,970
Well, thanks!

80
00:06:01,970 --> 00:06:04,590
Fantastic bamboo shoot boy!

81
00:06:06,350 --> 00:06:09,390
Twenty thousand...
Twenty thousand pilos?

82
00:06:10,350 --> 00:06:13,350
I mean, that's a high price for
some bamboo shoots, right?

83
00:06:13,350 --> 00:06:15,770
It'd be wrong of me to feel disappointed.

84
00:06:16,300 --> 00:06:18,320
Ryota, that lady...

85
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,860
Was she someone important?

86
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:22,030
"Important" doesn't begin to cover it!

87
00:06:22,470 --> 00:06:24,740
That was Eric Macy, the epicure.

88
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:29,950
Any food she approves of will fetch
a high price among the gourmet crowd!

89
00:06:29,950 --> 00:06:31,450
I see...

90
00:06:31,450 --> 00:06:34,210
Ryota, I'll skip all the formalities.

91
00:06:34,670 --> 00:06:37,130
Would you sign an exclusive
contract with us?

92
00:06:37,130 --> 00:06:38,670
A contract?

93
00:06:38,670 --> 00:06:43,220
Your bamboo shoots will soon
be a hot topic all over Secro.

94
00:06:43,220 --> 00:06:47,720
When that happens, I want the rights
to sell them as a branded product.

95
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:50,560
I want to sell them
as Ryota's Bamboo Shoots!

96
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:52,930
A branded product?

97
00:06:52,930 --> 00:06:56,850
That would be great for me,
but are they really worth

98
00:06:56,850 --> 00:06:58,020
They are!

99
00:06:58,020 --> 00:07:01,610
I'll pay a signing bonus in addition
to the cost of the shoots!

100
00:07:01,610 --> 00:07:02,860
All right.

101
00:07:02,860 --> 00:07:03,690
Huh?

102
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,700
I'll trust you with all of it.

103
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:08,240
Happy to partner with you, Erza.

104
00:07:09,410 --> 00:07:10,410
Same!

105
