Right!

111
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,650
What the heck was that?

112
00:07:37,650 --> 00:07:40,110
Sorry, but try not to get in our way.

113
00:07:40,110 --> 00:07:43,190
Princess Margaret is on the job.

114
00:07:43,190 --> 00:07:44,030
Princess?

115
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:52,200
You've got a princess, too?
This world is amazing.

116
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:54,500
She's using an air box.

117
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:55,790
An air box?

118
00:07:55,790 --> 00:08:00,630
Yeah. Do you know how monsters sometimes
don't drop anything after you kill them?

119
00:08:00,630 --> 00:08:05,260
Oh, yeah... For most people, I guess
the monsters in Nihonium don't...

120
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:09,800
It's apparently a useless dungeon
where nothing drops at all.

121
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:14,890
Yep. Recent research has revealed
that they're actually dropping air.

122
00:08:14,890 --> 00:08:16,310
Really?!

123
00:08:16,310 --> 00:08:20,730
Yeah. So we had the idea to put
the air in a box and sell it.

124
00:08:20,730 --> 00:08:24,860
And it's not just any air.
It's handmade by Princess Margaret!

125
00:08:24,860 --> 00:08:27,610
It's impressive that you had
the idea to sell air.

126
00:08:27,610 --> 00:08:30,280
Yep! It's our top product!

127
00:08:30,570 --> 00:08:33,700
For real? Is this the princess effect?

128
00:08:34,190 --> 00:08:35,950
Is that a magic cart?

129
00:08:35,950 --> 00:08:39,580
Yep. It lets us carry a lot
of air boxes at once.

130
00:08:39,580 --> 00:08:43,710
We can't have the princess coming
in and out of the dungeon too much.

131
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:48,970
Oh, yeah. Just being able to make fewer
trips would make it so much easier.

132
00:08:49,470 --> 00:08:51,140
A magic cart...

133
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:54,180
I've wanted one for ages,
but it'd be a major purchase.

134
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:57,100
I'll have to talk it over with Emily, too.

135
00:08:57,980 --> 00:09:03,980
So now I'm not sure whether to get
a new house or a magic cart first.

136
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:06,400
We should get a magic cart, then.

137
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:08,820
If we use it to save up money,

138
00:09:08,820 --> 00:09:11,160
we'll be able to afford a new place soon.

139
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:14,990
Good point.
Though we'd have to put off moving,

140
00:09:14,990 --> 00:09:17,080
and I'd feel bad doing that to you...

141
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:19,160
It's perfectly fine!

142
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:24,500
I like my life with you
in this little house very much!

143
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:26,670
Emily...

144
00:09:27,300 --> 00:09:28,420
You're right.

145
00:09:28,810 --> 00:09:32,220
I guess we'll be here
in the Emily house for a while longer.

146
00:09:32,220 --> 00:09:33,470
Yes!

147
00:09:33,470 --> 00:09:36,640
Well, then, should we go
to the magic cart shop tomorrow?

148
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:40,980
We'll be able to see
the owner's little girl, Olga, again!

149
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:44,440
Is that...

150
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,190
It's Olga!

151
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:53,280
Are you okay?

152
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:55,200
Daddy... Daddy has...

153
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,200
Did something happen
to your daddy?

154
00:09:57,200 --> 00:10:00,120
Daddy hasn't come home.

155
00:10:00,470 --> 00:10:01,580
What?

156
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:05,210
Did he tell you where he was going?

157
00:10:05,210 --> 00:10:09,630
I don't know. He said he was
going to pick flowers.

158
00:10:09,630 --> 00:10:10,760
Flowers?

159
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:16,050
The only place to get flower drops
around here is a dungeon called Arsenic.

160
00:10:16,050 --> 00:10:18,970
So there's a good chance
that's where he is.

161
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:22,560
Let's go to Arsenic!

162
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:24,230
Yes!

163
00:10:25,060 --> 00:10:27,400
MY UNIQUE SKILL MAKES ME OP EVEN AT LEVEL 1
I wonder how many there are...

164
