169
00:10:35,570 --> 00:10:37,320
ARSENIC LEVEL 1
So this is Arsenic.

170
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,120
ARSENIC LEVEL 1

171
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:43,500
The monsters here are called Danderocks,
and they don't move.

172
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:45,330
They don't attack, either.

173
00:10:45,330 --> 00:10:48,170
I see. Then we canâ€”

174
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:54,260
Or not. Looks like we have
to kill them after all.

175
00:10:55,470 --> 00:10:57,140
The bullet bounced off?!

176
00:10:57,140 --> 00:10:59,100
Yoda, stand back!

177
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:08,400
Of course! Between your increased power
and the strength of that hammer...

178
00:11:08,770 --> 00:11:10,360
Way to go, Emily!

179
00:11:12,190 --> 00:11:13,490
Let's hurry.

180
00:11:13,900 --> 00:11:18,410
ARSENIC LEVEL 10

181
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:23,160
There he is! That's Olga's father!

182
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,290
Are you okay?!

183
00:11:25,290 --> 00:11:26,670
Oh, no...

184
00:11:35,090 --> 00:11:36,180
He's asleep!

185
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,590
Hey, wake up!

186
00:11:39,180 --> 00:11:40,720
He's not waking up.

187
00:11:42,470 --> 00:11:44,390
E-Emily?

188
00:11:44,390 --> 00:11:48,350
He made Olga worry so much,
and we find out he's...

189
00:11:48,350 --> 00:11:50,770
Wake up right now!

190
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:54,030
What's going on?!

191
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:56,320
Oh, it's you two.

192
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:59,950
Darn it, I was having such a nice nap.

193
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:05,700
Daddy, you left your sweet little girl
behind to wander around?

194
00:12:06,330 --> 00:12:09,000
I-I apologize!

195
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:12,170
What in the world were you doing here?

196
00:12:12,170 --> 00:12:14,170
Olga was worried sick about you.

197
00:12:14,170 --> 00:12:18,800
I came to get parts for my incredible
new magic cart prototype.

198
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:22,260
Namely, Heavy Rocks and Light Rocks.

199
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:26,480
I caught the heavy rock,
but as for the light rock...

200
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:31,610
Well, the Danderocks blocked my path,
and I couldn't get anywhere.

201
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:35,280
A prototype?
The one you mentioned before?

202
00:12:35,710 --> 00:12:37,570
Look there. That's it.

203
00:12:38,990 --> 00:12:41,620
Is that rock... flying?!

204
00:12:41,620 --> 00:12:45,910
Light Rocks are lighter than air,
and they're rare monsters,

205
00:12:45,910 --> 00:12:47,660
so I just can't get one.

206
00:12:47,660 --> 00:12:49,500
I see.

207
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:51,580
It might be tough to do solo,

208
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:53,750
but I bet two people could handle it.

209
00:12:56,760 --> 00:13:00,340
You're light, Emily,
but your hammer's heavy!

210
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:03,260
A-Are you all right, Yoda?

211
00:13:03,260 --> 00:13:05,220
N-No problem!

212
00:13:05,220 --> 00:13:08,680
I got my strength up to rank S
in Nihonium last time.

213
00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:11,270
I'll try my best, too!

214
00:13:14,050 --> 00:13:16,980
Ah! This is what I needed!

215
00:13:17,900 --> 00:13:21,410
It's pretty, sure,
but what did you need that for?

216
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:23,820
Let's step outside for now.

217
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:30,160
There. We'll leave it be for a while
and watch what happens.

218
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:35,920
If it turns into a stray,
it'll float up again, won't it?

219
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:38,340
There was a ceiling in the dungeon,

220
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:40,420
but if it floats up from here...

221
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:42,630
Yes, that's the thing.

222
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:46,600
We'll just have to run in
and grab it before it flies off.

223
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:49,220
So it's all up to chance, huh?

224
00:13:49,220 --> 00:13:51,770
I wonder if there's anything I can do...

225
00:13:52,430 --> 00:13:54,440
Any minute now, I think.

226
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:58,400
Time to grab my drop!

227
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:07,120
Nope, we're not done yet!

228
00:14:10,290 --> 00:14:11,290
